          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Activation.",
                " Author's note:  Since chemical changes occuring in",
                " molecules where an atom is affected by an internally",
                " converted isomeric transition can be detected, it is",
                " possible to use the difference in the oxidation",
                " state of the metastable and ground state isomers in",
                " order to obtain its separation and therefore, an",
                " indirect measurement of activation cross-section",
                " ratio.",
                " Chemical oxidation of the radioactive materials (such",
                " as Te-121m and Te-121g) to telluric acid gives",
                " 'hexavalent' tellurium in both metastable and ground",
                " state species, whereas isomeric transition produces",
                " 'tetravalent' ground state species. ="
              ]
            }
          ],
